1.title: What does this library do?
1.content: You can upload multiple SVG files using the UPLOAD form - the library will process them and create one SVG file containing your icons as 'symbols'. These can be used inside your project similarly to a sprite file.

2.title: How can i import it into my project?
2.content: You can run npm i -D svg-icon-sprite to add the library as a dev dependency.
